00098         params.push_back(param);
00099

00101         param.Value = L"array-att-value-2";
00102         params.push_back(param);
00103 
00104         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( params.size() == 2 );
00105 
00106         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( array.PhysicalArraysAttributes().size() == 1 );
00107         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( array.PhysicalArraysAttributes()[0].Identifier() == "array1-id");
00108 
00109         ParameterNameValuePairVector::iterator it = array.PhysicalArraysAttributes()[0].Attributes().begin();
00110         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Name == L"array-att-name-1" );
00111         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Value == L"array-att-value-1" );
00112         ++it;
00113         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Name == L"array-att-name-2" );
00114         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( (*it).Value == L"array-att-value-2" );
00115         ++it;
00116         CPPUNIT_ASSERT (it == array.PhysicalArraysAttributes()[0].Attributes().end() );
00117 
00118         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( array.PhysicalArraysAttributes()[0].Attributes()[0].Name == L"array-att-name-1" );
00119         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( array.PhysicalArraysAttributes()[0].Attributes()[0].Value == L"array-att-value-1" );
00120         CPPUNIT_ASSERT( array.PhysicalArraysAttributes()[0].Attributes()[1].Name == L"array-att-name-2" );
